@QuizAppAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5226

### Get user profile
GET {{QuizAppAPI_HostAddress}}/api/user/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get user stats
GET {{QuizAppAPI_HostAddress}}/api/user/1/stats
Accept: application/json

###

### Get quiz categories
GET {{QuizAppAPI_HostAddress}}/api/quiz/categories
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all quizzes
GET {{QuizAppAPI_HostAddress}}/api/quiz
Accept: application/json

###

### Get only Math quizzes
GET {{QuizAppAPI_HostAddress}}/api/quiz?category=Math
Accept: application/json

###

### Start quiz 1 as user 1 (free quiz)
GET {{QuizAppAPI_HostAddress}}/api/quiz/1/start?userId=1
Accept: application/json

###

### Try to start premium quiz 3 as free user 1 (should fail with 403)
GET {{QuizAppAPI_HostAddress}}/api/quiz/3/start?userId=1
Accept: application/json

###

### Start premium quiz 3 as premium user 2 (should work)
GET {{QuizAppAPI_HostAddress}}/api/quiz/3/start?userId=2
Accept: application/json

###

### Submit answers for quiz 1
POST {{QuizAppAPI_HostAddress}}/api/quiz/1/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "answers": [
    { "questionId": 1, "selectedOption": "C" },
    { "questionId": 2, "selectedOption": "A" },
    { "questionId": 3, "selectedOption": "B" }
  ]
}

###